{"tid":268403,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"6428交叉8848 - 陳也","createTime":"2017-06-03T04:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T04:46:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66081e1971b443ae65823311b33d4a6593ae6310","tid":268403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T04:45:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20042558&amp;category_guid=vice&amp;sup_id=12187389&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170603\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20042558%26category_guid%3Dvice%26sup_id%3D12187389%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170603&d=Meg8eMkED75wBlDILqO4ujCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9a59ea93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20042558%26category_guid%3Dvice%26sup_id%3D12187389%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170603&h=d8c7927a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20042558&amp;category_guid=vice&amp;sup_id=12187389&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170603</a><br />\n<br />\n6428交叉8848 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n名采論壇&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n來到6428，6字頭的689，過去咁多年，年年都有今明兩日，48小時唔算長，689面懵懵搵窿捐，怕被人提起當年控訴屠夫政權，無得否認的報章聯署廣告再被曝光。跟UGL不同，無得抵賴，無得告人誹謗，無得鼎！若問689點睇6428？當然唔敢睇，心底虛怯，唔知習神幾時發功咬住唔like。伴君如伴虎，政協動物園裏只有一個神，其餘的心知肚明，都是飼料。<br />\n6428，今年交叉珠峰頂的8848。每年一度，向神山攻頂的最佳月份是五、六月。毋忘六四，到了六月，市民自動波全副武裝，到維園攻頂&hellip;&hellip;攻人數的頂。過去某些年，參與者共同進退，最高紀錄，由香港人創造的六四維園燭光悼念，坐爆企硬高達十五萬人！這兩三年，支聯會被揪秤杯葛，人數回落，號召到其他地區晒冷行動卻未算成功，借六四高調反枱，市民並未受落。維園，是64初心莫忘的象徵，在禮崩樂壞的今天，行禮還能如儀，不會被警察D你老母，不怕被警棍延伸，不必憂慮收到特首的律師信&hellip;&hellip;注意，只是暫時！再過N年難保香港被新香港人佔領，銅鑼灣比內地更內地，維園夜夜被大媽舞霸！六四記憶，從此只照亮手機。"},{"pid":"c3ea192e39cc8137321bbe90e05c63e735f84160","tid":268403,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T04:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170603/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170603%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=fa56408c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}